fulltitle: Buddy Rich Tonight Show May 1974 interview only
description: Buddy's performance was omitted when this show was recently rebroadcast. I am told it's due to high costs demanded by music licensing producers, and Carson Entertainment won't pay it. To whom do you suppose this refers - music licensing producers?
